parameters.query:
SELECT id AS ticket_id, text AS description, address, segment
FROM tickets
WHERE id = $1
LIMIT 1;

assignments.name: llm_prompt
assignments.value:
=Ты — модуль классификации обращений контакт-центра (F.I.R.E. Challenge). Верни СТРОГО валидный JSON по схеме (без markdown).

Текст обращения: {{ $json.description }}
Адрес/локация: {{ $json.address }}
Сегмент клиента: {{ $json.segment }}

Правила:
- type ∈ [Жалоба, Смена данных, Консультация, Претензия, Неработоспособность приложения, Мошеннические действия, Спам]
- sentiment ∈ [Позитивный, Нейтральный, Негативный]
- priority: целое 1..10
- lang ∈ [RU, KZ, ENG] (если не уверен — RU)
- summary: 1-2 предложения
- recommendation: 1-2 конкретных действия оператору/системе

parameters.query:
INSERT INTO ticket_ai (ticket_id, type, sentiment, priority, lang, summary, recommendation, confidence, updated_at)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, NOW())
ON CONFLICT (ticket_id) DO UPDATE SET
  type = EXCLUDED.type,
  sentiment = EXCLUDED.sentiment,
  priority = EXCLUDED.priority,
  lang = EXCLUDED.lang,
  summary = EXCLUDED.summary,
  recommendation = EXCLUDED.recommendation,
  confidence = EXCLUDED.confidence,
  updated_at = NOW()
RETURNING *;
UPDATE tickets SET status = 'enriched', updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = $1 RETURNING id, status;

UPDATE ticket_ai
SET lat = $2,
    lon = $3,
    geo_country = $4,
    geo_status = $5,
    updated_at = NOW()
WHERE ticket_id = $1
RETURNING *;

WITH
input AS (
  SELECT
    $1::uuid    AS ticket_id,
    $2::text    AS ai_type,
    $3::text    AS segment,
    $4::text    AS lang,
    $5::text    AS geo_status,
    $6::text    AS geo_country,
    $7::double precision AS lat,
    $8::double precision AS lon,
    ( $5 = 'OK' AND $6 = 'KZ' AND $7 IS NOT NULL AND $8 IS NOT NULL ) AS geo_ok
),
office AS (
  SELECT bu.id, bu.name,
         CASE WHEN (SELECT geo_ok FROM input)
              THEN ((bu.lat - (SELECT lat FROM input))^2 + (bu.lon - (SELECT lon FROM input))^2)
              ELSE 0
         END AS dist2,
         CASE WHEN NOT (SELECT geo_ok FROM input) THEN
           CASE WHEN (ascii(right((SELECT ticket_id FROM input)::text, 1)) % 2 = 0)
                THEN ((bu.name ILIKE '%Astana%' OR bu.name ILIKE '%Астана%')::int)
                ELSE ((bu.name ILIKE '%Almaty%' OR bu.name ILIKE '%Алматы%')::int)
           END
         ELSE 0 END AS pref
  FROM business_units bu
  WHERE (SELECT geo_ok FROM input)
     OR (bu.name ILIKE '%Astana%' OR bu.name ILIKE '%Астана%' OR bu.name ILIKE '%Almaty%' OR bu.name ILIKE '%Алматы%')
  ORDER BY
    CASE WHEN (SELECT geo_ok FROM input) THEN dist2 ELSE 0 END ASC,
    pref DESC,
    bu.id ASC
  LIMIT 1
),
bucket AS (
  SELECT
    office.id::text || '|' ||
    CASE WHEN (SELECT segment FROM input) ILIKE 'vip%' OR (SELECT segment FROM input) ILIKE 'prior%'
         THEN 'vip' ELSE 'mass' END || '|' ||
    CASE WHEN (SELECT ai_type FROM input) = 'Смена данных' THEN 'chief' ELSE 'any' END || '|' ||
    CASE WHEN (SELECT lang FROM input) IN ('KZ','ENG') THEN (SELECT lang FROM input) ELSE 'RU' END
    AS key
  FROM office
),
eligible AS (
  SELECT m.id, m.active_count
  FROM managers m, office, input
  WHERE m.office_id = office.id
    AND (NOT (input.segment ILIKE 'vip%' OR input.segment ILIKE 'prior%') OR m.skills ? 'VIP')
    AND (NOT (input.ai_type = 'Смена данных') OR m.position = 'Глав спец')
    AND (NOT (input.lang IN ('KZ','ENG')) OR m.skills ? input.lang)
  ORDER BY m.active_count ASC, m.id ASC
  LIMIT 2
),
pair AS (
  SELECT
    (array_agg(id ORDER BY active_count ASC, id ASC))[1] AS m1,
    (array_agg(id ORDER BY active_count ASC, id ASC))[2] AS m2
  FROM eligible
),
ensure_bucket AS (
  INSERT INTO rr_pointer(routing_bucket, last_manager_id, updated_at)
  SELECT bucket.key, NULL, NOW()
  FROM bucket
  ON CONFLICT (routing_bucket) DO NOTHING
  RETURNING routing_bucket
),
state AS (
  SELECT rp.routing_bucket, rp.last_manager_id
  FROM rr_pointer rp, bucket
  WHERE rp.routing_bucket = bucket.key
  FOR UPDATE
),
chosen AS (
  SELECT
    bucket.key AS routing_bucket,
    office.id AS office_id,
    pair.m1,
    pair.m2,
    CASE
      WHEN pair.m1 IS NULL THEN NULL
      WHEN pair.m2 IS NULL THEN pair.m1
      WHEN state.last_manager_id = pair.m1 THEN pair.m2
      WHEN state.last_manager_id = pair.m2 THEN pair.m1
      ELSE pair.m1
    END AS manager_id
  FROM bucket, office, pair, state
),
upd_rr AS (
  UPDATE rr_pointer
  SET last_manager_id = chosen.manager_id, updated_at = NOW()
  FROM chosen
  WHERE rr_pointer.routing_bucket = chosen.routing_bucket
    AND chosen.manager_id IS NOT NULL
  RETURNING rr_pointer.routing_bucket
),
ins_assign AS (
  INSERT INTO ticket_assignment(ticket_id, manager_id, office_id, assigned_at, routing_bucket)
  SELECT (SELECT ticket_id FROM input), chosen.manager_id, chosen.office_id, NOW(), chosen.routing_bucket
  FROM chosen
  ON CONFLICT (ticket_id) DO UPDATE
    SET manager_id = EXCLUDED.manager_id,
        office_id = EXCLUDED.office_id,
        assigned_at = EXCLUDED.assigned_at,
        routing_bucket = EXCLUDED.routing_bucket
  RETURNING *
),
upd_load AS (
  UPDATE managers
  SET active_count = active_count + 1
  WHERE id = (SELECT manager_id FROM chosen)
    AND (SELECT manager_id FROM chosen) IS NOT NULL
  RETURNING id, active_count
)
SELECT
  (SELECT ticket_id FROM input) AS ticket_id,
  ins_assign.manager_id,
  ins_assign.office_id,
  ins_assign.routing_bucket,
  (SELECT name FROM office) AS office_name,
  upd_load.active_count AS manager_active_count,
  -- echo back AI fields for response/UI
  (SELECT ai_type FROM input) AS ai_type,
  (SELECT segment FROM input) AS segment,
  (SELECT lang FROM input) AS lang,
  (SELECT geo_status FROM input) AS geo_status,
  (SELECT geo_country FROM input) AS geo_country,
  (SELECT lat FROM input) AS lat,
  (SELECT lon FROM input) AS lon
FROM ins_assign
LEFT JOIN upd_load ON upd_load.id = ins_assign.manager_id;
UPDATE tickets SET status = 'routed', updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = $1 RETURNING id, status;

parameters.responseBody:
={{ {
  ticket_id: $json.ticket_id,
  manager_id: $json.manager_id,
  office_id: $json.office_id,
  office_name: $json.office_name,
  routing_bucket: $json.routing_bucket,
  manager_active_count: $json.manager_active_count,
  ai: {
    type: $json.ai_type,
    segment: $json.segment,
    lang: $json.lang,
    sentiment: $('Map AI fields').item.json.sentiment,
    priority: $('Map AI fields').item.json.priority,
    summary: $('Map AI fields').item.json.summary,
    recommendation: $('Map AI fields').item.json.recommendation,
    confidence: $('Map AI fields').item.json.confidence
  },
  geo: {
    status: $json.geo_status,
    country: $json.geo_country,
    lat: $json.lat,
    lon: $json.lon
  }
} }}
